dels]] ** [[DNA topology]] ** [[DNA sequencing theory]] *[[Evolutionary developmental biology]] * [[Autopoiesis]] * [[Protein folding]] * [[Telomerase]] conformations and functions ''in vivo'' * [[Epigenetics]] * [[Interactomics]]<ref name="Faith2007"> {{cite journal | author = Faith, JJ | year = 2007 | title = Large-Scale Mapping and Validation of Escherichia coli Transcriptional Regulation from a Compendium of Expression Profiles | journal = [[PLoS Biology]] | volume = 5 | issue = 1 | pages = 54–66 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pbio.0050008 | pmid = 17214507 | pmc = 1764438 | display-authors = 1 | last2 = Hayete | first2 = Boris | last3 = Thaden | first3 = Joshua T. | last4 = Mogno | first4 = Ilaria | last5 = Wierzbowski | first5 = Jamey | last6 = Cottarel | first6 = Guillaume | last7 = Kasif | first7 = Simon | last8 = Collins | first8 = James J. | last9 = Gardner | first9 = Timothy S. }}</ref><ref name="Hayete2007"> {{cite journal |author1=Hayete, B |author2=Gardner, TS |author3=Collins, JJ | year = 2007 | title = Size matters: network inference tackles the genome scale | journal = [[Molecular Systems Biology]] | volume = 3 |issue = 1| pages = 77 | doi = 10.1038/msb4100118 | pmid = 17299414 | pmc = 1828748 }}</ref> * [[Cell signaling]] * [[Signal transduction|Signal transduction networks]] * [[neural net|Complex neural nets]] * [[Gene network|Genetic networks]] * [[Morphogenesis]] * [[Digital morphogenesis]] * [[Complex adaptive system]]s * [[Catastrophe theory|Topological models of morphogenesis]] * [[Population dynamics of fisheries]] * [[Epidemiology]] * [[Theoretical ecology]] * Immune system
