===Series 6 (2017)===
The sixth series started on 20 August 2017.<ref name="S6E1">{{Cite episode |title=Constable |series=Fake or Fortune? |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b092sh3q |accessdate=20 August 2017 |network= [[BBC Television]] |date=20 August 2017 |seriesno=6 |number=1 |transcript= |transcripturl= }}</ref> It was originally planned to have four episodes before one was postponed.<ref name="Giacometti">{{cite tweet|user=philipmould|number=906992186687983616|date=10 September 2017 |author= Philip Mould|title= Apology accepted. Next week's #fakeorfortune(Giacometti) is postponed pending further investigations.TX date to be announced. Repeat instead}}</ref>
